profile_positions.description:
Senior consultant, manager and co-owner of Banana hill consulting company that was founded in 2000. Specialising in the fields of:

          ► Research Management;
          ► Carbon Sequestration and Climate Change;
          ► Rural Energy Provision;
          ► Biofuel Crop Research;
          ► Web Development; and
          ► ICT4DEV.

Clients include Wageningen University, Van Hall Larenstein, FAO, ICCO, HIVOS, EOSTA, KIT, FACT, ILEIA,  Rhizosphere Research Products, the Netherlands Ministry of Foreign Affairs and the One Acre Fund. Assignments in Malawi⚑, Kenya⚑, Mozambique⚑, Guinea Bissau⚑, Benin⚑, and the Netherlands⚑.
